39766756_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dET9nflk97MQ7kNvgFAxMUS&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBfnHD9Vesa2eL7kNHZ5wJGCQD5dDwI3oWbyAhjQul_Ig&oe=670A5CD3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Thumbnail_Trailer_Shack August Update.png", "id": "2263072067378647", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974725_2263072070711980_2490880947384446619_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8s_2O51gkmwQ7kNvgGHnmWY&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDHGdtQM3sNlsNUjIdZevoMp74ZJ2LvhAnn_o7LP-EIxQ&oe=670A51E2"}, "display_name": "Pavlov Shack", "keywords": ["Shooter", "FPS", "multiplayer", "pvp", "combat"], "long_description": "Pavlov is a team-based multiplayer VR shooter with realistic weapon handling. Play a variety of game modes with over 65 interactable weapons and attachments in various environments.\n\nTeam up in a match of 5v5 in Search and Destroy, a classic uncompromising competitive game mode where you must attack or defend against a bomb objective.\n\nUse your detective skills to uncover the traitors in a casual murder mystery gameplay with various player roles in TTT.\n\nNeutralize a monster that escaped captivity in an asymmetrical 1 vs. 9 game.\n\nOperate vehicles such as 4\u00d74s or tanks with intuitive driving controls in a WWII match to defend your homeland in Stalingrad.\n\nPlay hundreds of community made mods. \n\nBite the bullet, grit your teeth, and queue up.", "short_description": "Multiplayer shooter in VR with realistic weapon mechanics, features 5 vs 5 competitive and social game modes."}]}, "developer_name": "Vankrupt Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://cdn.pavlov-vr.com/privacy_policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.vankrupt.com/eula.html", "publisher_name": "Vankrupt Games", "support_website_url": "http://pavlovwiki.com/index.php/Main_Page", "website_url": "https://www.vankrupt.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_ra